    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the naturally aspirated 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a broad torque curve through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, supported by a multi-link rear suspension and upgraded Bilstein dampers for neutral handling. Critical preventative maintenance is addressed, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent thermal management during spirited driving. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain sharp, making this a driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
