    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super well-maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner! It drives like a charm and looks great inside and out. If you're looking for a reliable, comfy ride that's been treated with love, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
